  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个基础设施架构图，核心是三个Ingress Controller，它们要统一接入到一个Worker Node上，然后这个节点再向下连接三个底层节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "SI",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个Ingress Controller是C1、C2、C3对吧？然后中间的Worker Node你打算怎么命名？还有下面三个节点是Worker Node还是Redis Cache？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "SI",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "中间的叫SI，是Infra_WorkerNode。下面三个里M1、M2是Worker Node，M3比较特殊，是Redis Cache。整个结构我想用三个子图来组织。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SI",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画出三个Ingress Controller C1、C2、C3，放在第一个子图里，标注为Infra_RedisCache。然后中间放SI节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "SI",
        "ROS2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "C1到C3的位置没问题，但子图名称我确认一下——上面这个子图应该叫Infra_RedisCache吗？等等，让我再想想，其实ROS2这个子图放Ingress Controller，但标签用Infra_RedisCache是业务上的命名约定。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ROS2",
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "了解了，我继续画第二个子图HWI，里面放SI节点，标签也用Infra_RedisCache。然后第三个子图Hardware放M1、M2、M3，标签是Infra_EtcdCluster。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HWI",
        "SI",
        "Hardware",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Hardware子图的标签是Infra_EtcdCluster，但里面的M1、M2是Infra_WorkerNode，M3是Infra_RedisCache，这个混合没关系吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Hardware",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题，节点类型和子图标签可以不一致。现在我来画连接关系：C1、C2、C3都单向指向SI，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "SI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，三个Ingress Controller都是单向连接到SI。然后SI到M1、M2、M3是双向的，因为Worker Node和Redis Cache之间会有双向通信。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "SI",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "连接画好了：C1--SI、C2--SI、C3--SI都是单向，SI<--M1、SI<--M2、SI<--M3都是双向箭头。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "SI",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，HWI子图的标签我搞错了。SI所在的子图标签应该是Infra_RedisCache，但我刚才说的是HWI，这个命名没问题，但让我确认一下——HWI子图里只有SI一个节点，标签是Infra_RedisCache，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HWI",
        "SI"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，HWI子图包含SI节点，标签是Infra_RedisCache。这个和ROS2子图的标签一样，都是Infra_RedisCache，你确定要重复吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HWI",
        "ROS2",
        "SI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "确定，业务上这两个层都属于Redis Cache基础设施。不过ROS2子图的名字我确认一下，应该是ROS2对吧？三个Ingress Controller属于ROS2控制平面。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ROS2",
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我最终确认一遍结构：ROS2子图（Infra_RedisCache）包含C1、C2、C3；HWI子图（Infra_RedisCache）包含SI；Hardware子图（Infra_EtcdCluster）包含M1、M2、M3。连接关系也全部画好了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ROS2",
        "HWI",
        "Hardware",
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "SI",
        "M1",
