      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "布局已调整为TB方向，ROS2在上，HWI居中，Hardware在下。整个流程从三个Ingress Controller流入SI，再双向连接到三个底层节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
